sourcesContent: import { Button, Col, Row } from 'antd' import React from 'react' import Pencil from '../../assets/img/iconos/edit-24px.svg' import Delete from '../../assets/img/iconos/delete-24px.svg' export default function Competencias(props) { const {data} = props; return ( data.map((data,index) => {data.competencia} {data.nivel} ) ) }
